{"tid":98982,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"輸到咩都無哂","createTime":"2017-01-28T21:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T13:17:44.000Z","uid":80080,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5fa19d84871876c4ae60f6e663890fdd74c7ee2","tid":98982,"uid":80080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T21:49:44.000Z","msg":"相信每個賭仔都曾經諗過自己係與眾不同 <br />\n自己就算唔係賭神 都唔會輸好甘<br />\n成年前 仲係學生既我 贏左人地幾個月糧 <br />\n我就瘋狂亂洗錢 同將注碼提升<br />\n去到最後 一蚊都無<br />\n以為有本就可以翻身 <br />\n點知上年原來係我人生最好運<br />\n而加點賭都輸 好後悔學識賭波賭馬打麻雀 入賭場<br />\n如果你見到呢個post希望你可以知到你有運就好用盡 無運果陣就好收手<br />\n祝雞年人人有運"},{"pid":"6b047a6f3b212eaa4afb2a4f2fbef8ad55a4db9a","tid":98982,"uid":15482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:00:59.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6a0d187866bf5227d435188f5d4564e1d45661","tid":98982,"uid":5179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:23:35.000Z","msg":"其實冇所謂運氣<br />\n你連贏得十場就會輸返十場(假設只有兩個項目)<br />\n只係你買中連贏十場覺得自己好好運咁解"},{"pid":"ef7aa308dad045b20dc22af08f6d44888b638e63","tid":98982,"uid":80080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:25:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實冇所謂運氣<br />\n你連贏得十場就會輸返十場(假設只有兩個項目)<br />\n只係你買中連贏十場覺得自己好好運咁解</blockquote><br />\n連輸十場了"},{"pid":"15508cec52c9ec7b7d8c6842c5bbf74b1891590e","tid":98982,"uid":80080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝"},{"pid":"8a22ffb0dbd68055e70595e0f89cd4833686648c","tid":98982,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:40:27.000Z","msg":"贏過輸過咪當打個和囉<br />\n以前賭細啲囉"},{"pid":"a501db414dc8265327492ddd95d35a17006b7701","tid":98982,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T22:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>贏過輸過咪當打個和囉<br />\n以前賭細啲囉</blockquote><br />\n以